word !important; height: 6px; color: inherit;\"><section data-bcless=\"darken\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 230, 217); border-image-source: none; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left;\"></section><section data-bcless=\"darken\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 230, 217); border-image-source: none; width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right;\"></section></section><section data-bcless=\"darken\" style=\"margin: -1px 5px; padding: 4px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 230, 217); border-image-source: none; background-color: rgb(254, 251, 245);\"><section class=\"135brush\" data-bcless=\"darken\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 230, 217); border-image-source: none;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">纪念爱因斯坦广义相对论诞辰100周年</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; te