30\" alt=\"丨邀请函 | 未来论坛年度盛宴：致敬爱因斯坦，致敬科学！\" style=\"margin: 1em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 4px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“未来论坛”一个关注科技创新的民间公益组织；一个承载人类科技梦想，用前沿科技改变世界，解读人类社会未来趋势的思想平台。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“未来论坛2016年会”，邀请全球科学、经济、教育、艺术、政治等各界精英及有识之士，共襄盛举，分享人类智慧成果，跨越思想和心灵的疆界，同时将成立第一个属于中国的诺贝尔奖——“未来科学前沿大奖”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">站在人类历史新的临界点上，眺望未来，引领未来，我们邀您共同开创人类认知新百年。真诚期待您的莅临，谢谢！</p><p><br/></p><section class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"86043\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; border: 0px currentcolor; border-image-source: none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"135brush\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 15px 20px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgb(237, 237, 237); border-image-source: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-stretch: normal;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">主办单位：未来论坛 </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">指导单位：中国科学技术协会</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">执行机构：新盟国际</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">战略合作：毕马威中国 &nbsp;方达律师事务所 &nbsp;英菲尼迪 <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">合作伙伴：盖茨基金会 &nbsp;联想 &nbsp;中金公司 &nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px;\">嘉实基金 &nbsp;京东</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 17px;\">支持媒体：爱奇艺 &nbsp;凤凰网 &nbsp;环球科学 &nbsp;新浪科技 &nbsp;一点资讯 &nbsp;</span></p></section></section><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">具体议程如下（</span><a href=\"http://baoming.futureforum.org.cn/nianhui\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"未来论坛年会报名\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">点击报名</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">）：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">人类认知新百年</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-size: 20px;\">未来论坛·2016年会</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">2016年1月17日中国·北京·国贸大酒店</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">2015年12月21日更新<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/>所有嘉宾以实际到场为准</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　07:30 - 08:30</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　注册签到</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　08:30 - 08:40</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　开场视频：引领未来　　</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;08:40 - 08:50</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 　开幕致辞</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　致辞嘉宾：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　丁健，金沙江创投董事总经理，未来论坛创始理事，未来论坛首届轮值主席</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　第一章</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　创新引领未来</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　创新，是催生惊世变革的核心力量与原始动力，更是一个企业、国家、民族乃至整个人类希望之所在。创新，是一种精神，更是一种态度。它来自于思维的变革，引导人们探索未知，实现梦想，改变未来！</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　08:50 - 09:05</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主题演讲1</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　技术创新与模式创新</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　李彦宏，百度公司创始人、董事长兼首席执行官，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　09:05 - 09:20</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主题演讲2</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　创新是真正的核心力量</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　杨元庆，联想集团董事长兼首席执行官，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　09:20 - 09:35</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主题演讲3</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　制度与法律创新</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　高西庆，清华大学法学院郑裕彤讲席教授，中国投资有限责任公司原副董事长、总经理兼首席投资官，未来论坛咨询委员会委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　09:35 - 09:50</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主题演讲4</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　教育与科研创新</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　饶毅，北京大学终身讲席教授、北京大学校务委员会副主任，兼北京生命科学研究所资深研究员，未来论坛科学家委员会委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　09:50&nbsp;-10:40</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　创新对话</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主持人：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　徐小平，真格基金创始人，新东方联合创始人，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　对话嘉宾：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　冯仑，万通集团主席，万通投资控股股份有限公司董事长，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　JefferyManber，Managing Director, Nanoracks</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　王敏，中央美术学院设计学院院长</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　John Maeda，Kleiner Perkins Caufield&amp; Byers设计合伙人，罗德岛设计学院前院长</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　朱云来，著名金融人士，未来论坛咨询委员会委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　邓锋，北极光创始人兼董事总经理，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　第二章</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　新趋势、新技术、新投资</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　雨果曾说：与有待创造的东西相比，已经创造出来的东西是微不足道的。进入21世纪以来，新的一轮科技革命风起云涌。未来，人们所关注的是什么？人工智能？精准医疗？还是时空穿越梦想成真？新的技术一日千里，这将催生产业的重大变革。与此同时，也将深度融合、广泛渗透到人类社会的各个层面。新的、多元化的投资模式使人类发展的成长空间豁然开朗，全新的未来已经呼之欲出。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　10:40 - 10:55</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主题演讲1</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　Aubrey de Grey，SENS研究基金会首席科学家</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　10:55 - 11:10</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主题演讲2</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　沈向洋，微软全球执行副总裁，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　11:10 - 11:25</span></p><p><span style=