span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　第四章</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　未来之路</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　科技不兴，其国必弱。美国、欧洲和日本的科技发展势如风雷，中国科学的未来路在何方？重视科技教育及人才的引进与培养，重视新型科技产业的发展。中国需要走一条“自主创新”、“可持续发展”的科学道路。方向已定，唯有砥砺前行！</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　16:20 - 17:10</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　对话未来</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主持人：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　饶毅，北京大学终身讲席教授、北京大学校务委员会副主任，兼北京生命科学研究所资深研究员，未来论坛科学家委员会委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　对话嘉宾：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　未来科学大奖捐赠人</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　丁健，金沙江创投董事总经理，未来论坛创始理事，未来论坛首届轮值主席</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　李彦宏，百度公司创始人、董事长兼首席执行官，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　沈南鹏，红杉资本全球执行合伙人，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　张磊，高瓴资本集团董事长兼首席执行官，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　邓锋，北极光创始人兼董事总经理，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　徐小平，真格基金创始人，新东方联合创始人，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　17:10 - 17:20</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　视频：科学改变未来</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　17:20 - 17:30</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　未来科学大奖成立仪式</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主持人：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　武红，新盟国际总裁兼创始人，未来论坛发起人兼秘书长</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　第五章</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　创客“生”与“死”· 沙龙之夜</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　创业九死一生，折戟沉沙后如何卷土重来？几年过去，陷于瓶颈，或上市遥遥无期，又该如何面对？展望未来，生命科学、人工智能、环保等各领域会有怎样的突破？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　19:30 - 21:30</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　高峰对话：创新与创业</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　主持人：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　杨守彬，丰厚资本创始合伙人，黑马投资学院院长，中国青年天使会秘书长</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　对话嘉宾：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　徐小平，真格基金创始人、新东方联合创始人，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　视频致辞：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　戴雷博士，东风英菲尼迪总经理</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　嘉宾主持：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　王淮，线性资本创始合伙人，未来论坛青年行动小组委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　讨论嘉宾：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　李柏霖，通邮集团董事长，未来论坛创始理事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　山世光，中科院计算所研究员，未来论坛青年行动小组委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　王俊，碳云智能创始人、CEO，未来论坛青年行动小组委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　余凯，Horizon Robotics创始人，未来论坛青年行动小组委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　赵勇，格灵深瞳联合创始人，未来论坛青年行动小组委员</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　吴文达，比尔及梅琳达盖茨基金会副主任</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">　　未来论坛2016年会活动指定用车：英菲尼迪</span></p>', '借此爱因斯坦广义相对论诞生100周年之际，我们非常荣幸并诚挚地邀请您参加将于2016年1月17日（周日）在北京举办的 “未来论坛2016年会•人类认知新百年”。', '1', '未来论坛', '1', '', '丨未来•邀请函丨未来论坛年度盛宴：致敬爱因斯坦，致敬科学！', '', '借此爱因斯坦广义相对论诞生100周年之际，我们非常荣幸并诚挚地邀请您参加将于2016年1月17日（周日）在北京举办的 “未来论坛2016年会•人类认知新百年”。');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for `people`
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `people`;
CREATE TABLE `people` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `category` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `name_zh-cn` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `name_en` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `desc1_zh-cn` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `desc2_zh-cn` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `note_zh-cn` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `quote_zh-cn` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `desc1_en` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `desc2_en` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note_en` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quote_en` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=49 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of people
-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('4', 'chenxun', '1', '陈恂', 'Eric CHEN', '科技创业者和投资人', '', '现任美国硅谷华人科技创业非盈利组织华源科技（HYSTA）的董事长，也在多家美国和中国上市或私有的科技公司担任董事。', '未来其实是孕育在人的今天的行为、人的今天的智慧当中。', 'Technological Entrepreneur and Investor', '', 'Current chairman science and technology entrepreneurship non-profit organization Huayuan Technology (HYSTA) based in Silicon Valley and managing director of multiple private technology companies listed in the United States or China.', 'The future is actually bred in the wisdom of the people of today.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('5', 'dengfeng', '1', '邓锋', 'Feng DENG', '北极光创始人兼董事总经理', '', '拥有多项计算机结构和IC设计方面的美国专利。他在风险投资、计算机、通讯和数据网络产业有超过20年的技术和管理经验。', '我觉得科技对人最大的影响就是把我们的人生延长', 'Founder and Managing Director of Northern Light Venture Capital', '', 'Owns multiple American computer structure and Integrated Circuit Design patents. Has more than 20 years of technical and managerial experience in venture capital, computer science, communications and data networks.', 'The greatest impact of technology on mankind is its ability to extend our lives.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('6', 'dinghong', '4', '丁洪', 'Hong DING', '物理学家', '中国科学院物理所研究员', '北京凝聚态国家实验室首席科学家', '随着经济实力的提升，未来10年将会是中国科技发展的‘黄金10年’。', 'Physicist', 'Researcher at the Institute of Physics, Chinese Academy of Sciences', 'Chief Scientist at Beijing National Laboratory for Condensed Matter', 'Driven by an increase in economic power, the next 10 years will be the golden years of China\'s science and technology.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('7', 'dingjian', '1', '丁健', 'James DING', '金沙江创投董事总经理', '', '1993年创立美国亚信公司，并领导亚信成为第一家在美国纳斯达克上市的中国科技公司。目前兼任百度公司独立董事，华谊兄弟独立董事。', '未来的几十年内，人工智能将超越人脑', 'Managing Director of GSR Ventures', '', 'Founded AsiaInfo in 1993, and lead AsiaInfo to become the first Chinese technology company listed on NASDAQ. Currently serves as an independent director for Baidu and Huayi Brothers.', 'Over the next few decades, artificial intelligence will surpass the human brain');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('8', 'fangfang', '1', '方方', 'Fang FANG', '水木投资集团创始人兼董事长', '', '曾任摩根大通亚洲区投资银行副主席和中国投资银行首席执行官，及北京控股有限公司副总裁等职务。', '互联网会给我们打来巨大的机会和挑战。', 'Founder and Chairman of the Board of Waterwood Investment', '', 'Former Vice Chairman of Investment Banking at JP Morgan Asia and former CEO of Investment Banking at JP Morgan\'s China division. Vice President of Beijing Enterprises Holdings Limited.', 'The Internet is both an opportunity and a challenge. ');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('9', 'fenglun', '1', '冯仑', 'Lun FENG', '万通集团主席', '万通投资控股股份有限公司董事长', '曾担任中城联盟轮值主席、中国不动产商会副会长、中国房地产研究会副会长等职务。企业界称他为“商界思想家”，地产界称他为 “学者型”开发商', '互联网能够让陌生人开始交往，人和人之间开口说话容易了。', 'President of Vantone Group', 'Chairman of Board of Directors of Vantone Holdings Co., Ltd.', 'Former Chairman of the China City Federation, Vice President of the China Real Estate Chamber of Commerce, Vice President of the China Real Estate Research Assocation.', 'The Internet is the missing connection between strangers.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('10', 'gaoxiqing', '2', '高西庆', 'Xiqing GAO', '清华大学教授', '前中投副董事长总经理', '美国杜克大学校董，清华大学法学院、对外经济贸易大学法学院兼职教授、博士生导师，美国杜克大学客座教授曾任中国投资有限责任公司副董事长兼总经理。', '互联网忽然一夜之间影响到了每一个家里。', 'Professor of Tsinghua University', 'Former Vice Chairman of China Investment Corporation', 'On the Board of Trustees for Duke University and Tsinghua University Law School. Part-time Professor at UIBE Law School and visiting professor at Duke University. Former Vice Chairman and General Manager of China Investment Co. Ltd.', 'Overnight, the Internet impacted every household.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('11', 'hechuan', '4', '何川', 'Chuan HE', '美国芝加哥大学化学系教授', '美国霍华德·休斯医学研究所研究员', '北京大学化学与分子工程学院长江讲座教授', '', 'Professor at the Department of Chemistry, University of Chicago', 'Researcher at The Howard Huges Medical Institute', 'Professor at Peking University\'s School of Chemistry and Molecular Engineering', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('12', 'kangdian', '2', '康典', 'Dian KANG', '新华人寿保险有限公司董事长', '新华人寿保险有限公司执行董事', '新华人寿保险股份有限公司董事长、执行董事。曾任深圳发展银行股份有限公司监事会主席、时瑞投资管理有限公司董事长等职位。', '这是个变革与创新的时代。', 'Chairman of the Board of NCI', 'Executive Director of NCI', 'Chairman and Executive Director of Xinhua Life Insurance Company. Served a Chairman of the Board of Supervisors for Shenzhen Devleopment Bank Co Ltd', 'This is an era of change and innovation.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('13', 'liaoxiaoqi', '2', '廖晓淇', 'Xiaoqi LIAO', '国贸董事长', '原中国商务部副部长', '中国国际贸易中心有限公司董事长、中国十一届全国政协委员。曾任商务部副部长、中央纪委和对外经济贸易部处长。', '互联网的发展趋势是不可逆转的', 'Chairman of China World Trade Center', 'Former Vice Minister of Department of Commerce of China', 'Chairman of China International Trade Center Co Ltd, member of the CPPCC National Committee. Served as Deputy Minister of Commerce, and Director of the Central Commission for Discipline Inspection and Ministry of Foreign Economic Relations and Trade.', 'The development of the Internet is irreversible.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('14', 'libolin', '1', '李柏霖', 'Bolin LI', '通邮集团董事长', '', '金融信息技术创新联盟副理事长，常春藤中国论坛副理事长，互联网金融千人会副秘书长。信息安全、数据管理、移动通讯与支付、互联网与供应链金融等领域的专家', '有很多方面的突破是以往难以想象的，今天都变成了现实', 'President of ATMU', '', 'Vice President of the Financial Information Technology and Innovation Alliance, Vice Chairman of the Ivy China Forum, Vice Secretary General of Internet Financial Assistance. Expert in the field of information security, data management, mobile communications and payments, Internet and supply china finance.', 'Breakthroughs that were difficult to imagine in the past has today become a reality.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('16', 'lijiange', '2', '李剑阁', 'Jiange LI', '孙冶方经济科学基金会理事长', '', '孙冶方经济科学基金会理事长、中央汇金投资有限责任公司副董事长。曾任中国国际金融有限公司董事长、国务院发展研究中心副主任等职位。', '历史的转折点它叫做奇点，离我们已经不远了。', 'Director-General of Sun Yefang Foundation', '', 'Vice Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Economic Science Foundation of China. Served as Chairman of the China International Capital Co, Deputy Director of the State Council Development Research Center.', 'The singular turning point of history is now not far away from us.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('17', 'liyanhong', '1', '李彦宏', 'Robin LI', '百度公司创始人', '百度公司董事长兼首席执行官', '全面负责百度公司的战略规划和运营管理。2013年，当选第十二届全国政协委员，兼任第十一届中华全国工商业联合会副主席等职务。', '创新不是某一家公司的事情，而是很多公司、很多优秀人才相互激发、相互鼓励、相互促进、甚至相互竞争的过程，这样才会导致创新不断发生。', 'Founder of Baidu', 'CEO & President of Baidu', 'Elected to the 12th CPPCC National Committee and the 11th Vice Chairman of the China Federation of Industry and Commerce amongst other duties.', 'Innovation is not the business of a single company, but of mulitple companies. Only through a combination of mutual encouragement, inspiration, talent, competition and promotion can innovation occur.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('18', 'raoyi', '4', '饶毅', 'Yi RAO', '神经科学博士', '北京大学生命科学学院前院长', '北京大学终身讲席教授、北京大学校务委员会副主任，兼北京生命科学研究所资深研究员。曾任北大生命科学学院院长。', '要改善我国的科学，不仅需要改革体制，而且需要改进文化。', 'Ph. D in Neurology', 'Director of the Life Sciences Department at Peking University', 'Tenured professor at Beijing University, Director of Peking University Affairs Committee, Senior Fellow at the Institute of Beijing Life Science Research, Director of Beijing Zeng Ren Life Sciences University.', 'To improve the science of our country, we not only need to reform the system but also improve its culture.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('19', 'shanshiguang', '8', '山世光', 'Shiguang SHAN', '博士', '研究员(教授)', '中科院计算所智能信息处理重点实验室常务副主任', '真正的国际一流就像百米赛场一样，需要不断打破已有的世界纪录（the state of the art），创造属于我们的新纪录。', 'Ph. D', 'Researcher (Professor)', 'Executive Vice Director of the Laboratory of Intelligent Information Processing at the Chinese Academy of Sciences', 'International science is like a 100 meter race: we have to constantly try and break the existing world record (the most state of the art science and technology) in order to create our own new record.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('20', 'shennanpeng', '1', '沈南鹏', 'Neil SHEN', '红杉资本全球执行合伙人', '', '红杉资本全球执行合伙人，携程旅行网和如家连锁酒店的创始人。福布斯2012-2015年度全球最佳投资人榜单中排名最高的华人投资者。', '互联网的发展不仅仅早已改变今天的生活方式，而且还再改变未来的生活方式', 'Co-Founder and Executive Partner of Sequoia Capital China', '', 'Global Executive Partner of Sequoia Capital, Founder of CTrip and Hotels. Highest ranked Chinese investor on the Forbes 2012-2015 annual Global Best Investor list.', 'The development of the Internet has not only changed the way of our current lives but also changes the way of life in the future.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('21', 'shiyigong', '2', '施一公', 'Yigong SHI', '中国科学院院士', '清华大学生命科学学院院长', '清华大学副校长、美国科学院、美国艺术与科学院外籍院士，结构生物学家，长江讲座教授，国家杰出青年基金获得者。主要从事细胞凋亡及膜蛋白两个领域的研究', '中国真的需要一场文化的革命，真正意义上的文化创新与传承。', 'Academician of Chinese Academy of Sciences', 'President of School of Life Sciences of Tsinghua University', 'Vice President of Tsinghua University, Academician and Structural Biologist at the United States Academy of Sciences and the American Academy of Arts and Sciences. Professor of the Yangtze River and recipient of the National Outstanding Youth Fund Award. Mainly engaged in two areas of research: cell apoptosis and membrane protein.', 'China really needs a cultural revolution in the true sense of cultural innovation and heritage.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('22', 'tiangang', '4', '田刚', 'Gang TIAN', '普林斯顿大学数学系教授', '中国科学院院士', '', '', 'Professor of Mathematics, Princeton University', 'Academician of Chinese Academy of Sciences', '', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('23', 'wanghuai', '8', '王淮', 'Harry WANG', '线性资本创始合伙人', '', '浙江大学计算机系学士，斯坦福大学管理科学和工程专业硕士', '', 'Co-Founder of Linear Venture', '', 'Received a Bachelors degree in Computer Science from Stanford University, a Masters in Science Management and Engineering from Zhejiang University', 'Making something great yourself is different from being part of something great.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('24', 'wangjun', '8', '王俊', 'Jun WANG', '华大基因CEO', '华大基因研究院院长', '教授，博士生导师，国家杰出青年基金获得者，973首席科学家，前深圳华大基因CEO?兼研究院院长。', '能够确确实实平衡去控制自己的力量，最终达到人和世界有效共存，是人类将面临的一个问题。', 'Founder of iCarbonx', 'Director of BGI', 'Professor, Doctor, recipient of the National Outstanding Youth Fund award, Former Shenzhen Hua Da CEO.', 'To balance their own strength and eventually effectively coexist is a problem humanity will face.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('25', 'wangxiaodong', '4', '王晓东', 'Xiaodong WANG', '美国国家科学院院士', '', '北京生命科学研究所资深研究员', '科学史上的每一次重大发现，都极大地拓宽了人类视野，改变了人类对自然界及人类自身的认识，不仅极大推动了科学自身的发展和技术的巨大进步，也对文学、艺术、哲学等产生了深远的影响。', 'Academician of American National Academy of Sciences', '', 'Senior Research Fellow at the Beijing Institute of Life Sciences', 'Every major discovery in the history of science has greatly broadened the human vision, changed the human awareness of nature and human beings and not only greatly prompted a great progress in science and technology development but also has far-reaching influences on literature, art and philosophy.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('26', 'wuhong', '1', '武红', 'Cathy WU', '新盟国际公关公司创始合伙人', '新盟国际公关顾问公司总裁', '中国国际公关协会公司委员会理事，中国女性俱乐部副理事长，中国国际另类投资协会秘书长', '未来论坛是一个承载人类科技梦想，用科技改变世界的公益平台。', 'Co-Founder New Alliance Consulting International', 'President of New Alliance Consulting International', 'Director of China International Public Relations Assocation Inc, Vice President of the Chinese Women\'s Club, the Secretary General of the China International Alternative Investment Assocation', 'The Future Forum is a dream of human science and technology, using technology to change the world\'s public platform.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('27', 'wuying', '1', '吴鹰', 'Ying WU', '中泽嘉盟投资基金董事长', 'UT斯达康创始人', '2000年3月3日，UT斯达康公司在美国上市，吴鹰本人名列美国《商业周刊》评选的50位亚洲之星之一。 2006年11月创立私募股权投资机构中泽嘉盟投资有限公司', '我们是希望未来论坛对于未来的研究进行探索。 ', 'Chairman of Jiameng Investment Fund', 'Founder of UTStarcom', 'On March 3, 2000 UTStarcom became listed in the United States and Wu was listed as one of BusinessWeeks 50 Stars of Asia. In November 2006, he created Zejia Union Investment Limited.', 'We hope that the Future Forum is for future research.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('28', 'xiazhihong', '4', '夏志宏', 'Jeff XIA', '数学家', '美国西北大学终身教授', '北京大学数学科学学院长江学者讲座教授与博士生导师', '', 'Mathematician', 'Tenured Professor of Northwestern University', 'Professor, Doctor and Changjiang Scholar at the Peking University School of Mathematical Sciences', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('29', 'xiexiaoliang', '4', '谢晓亮', 'Sunney XIE', '美国国家科学院院士', '', '哈佛大学Mallinckrodt 讲席教授北京大学生物动态光学成像中心主任', '科学研究是我的嗜好，不断创新是我的追求，造福人类是我的愿望。', 'Academician at American National Academy of Sciences', '', 'Mallinckrodt Professor at Harvard University and Director of the Center for Biodynamic Optical Imaging at Peking University', 'Scientific research is my hobby, continuous innovation is my pursuit and the benefit of mankind is my desire.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('30', 'xuxiaoping', '1', '徐小平', 'Bob XU', '真格基金创始人', '新东方联合创始人', '2006年，随着新东方成功上市，徐小平创立真格基金，开始为中国青年创业者提供早期资金支持，先后投资世纪佳缘、兰亭集势、聚美优品等；', '未来是需要呼唤的，未来是需要拥抱的，未来论坛把一群想拥抱未来的人，聚集在一起，', 'Founder of ZhenFund', 'Co-Founder of New Oriental', 'In 2006, with the successful listing of New Oriental, Xu founded ZhenFund and started to provide early financial support to young Chinese entrepreneurs. Successful investments include Jumei, Jiayuan and Lightinthebox amongst others.', 'The future is something we need to call and embrace. The Future forum is for a group of people who want to embrace the future together.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('31', 'yangyuanqing', '1', '杨元庆', 'Yuanqing YANG', '联想集团董事长兼CEO', '', '成功领导联想收购IBM的PC事业部，并购IBM x86服务器以及摩托罗拉移动业务。2004年和2012年“CCTV中国经济年度人物”，2013年《巴伦周刊》全球30位最佳CEO之一', '我特别喜欢跟油脂与创新，乐于创新的企业同道们，在交流中互相启发交流思想，碰撞火花', 'President and CEO of Lenovo', '', 'Successful leadership of Lenovo\'s acquisition of PC\'s IBM division, the acquisition of the X86 IBM server and the Motorola mobile business. Was named one of the CCTV\'s China Economic Figures in 2004 and 2012. Was named the World\'s Top CEO in Barron\'s Magazine in 2013.', 'I especially like using grease and innovation and the exchange of mutual inspirations and ideas to spark ideas.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('32', 'yixiqun', '2', '衣锡群', 'Xiqun YI', '中国股权投资基金协会常务副会长', '', '中国股权投资基金协会常务副会长.?曾任北京市政协委员、京泰实业有限公司董事长、北京控股有限公司董事长等职位。', '就是所有的人都感到，他们周围的一切都在发生变化', 'Vice President of China Association of Private Equity ', '', 'Vice President of China Equity Investment Fund Assocation, President of the Beijing Municipal People\'s Political Consultative Conference, Chairman of the Board of Directors of Beijing Tai Industrial Co Ltd', 'Change is happening and everyone can feel it around them.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('33', 'yufeng', '1', '虞锋', 'David YU', '云锋基金发起人、基金主席', '', '与阿里巴巴董事局主席马云联合发起，中国唯一由成功创业者、企业家和行业领袖共同创立的私募云锋基金。同时担任华谊兄弟董事，上海广电电气董事', '加入未来论坛吧，让我们一起思考未来，漫步未来，洞见未来', 'Founder and Chairman of Yunfeng Capital', '', 'Launched China\'s only private equity fund consisting of successful entrepreneurs and industry leaders alongside Alibaba\'s Jack Ma. Also Director of Huayi Brothers Shanghai and the Director of Shanghai\'s Radio and Television.', 'Join the Future Forum so we can think about the future and walk ahead, getting a peek of what\'s to come.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('34', 'yukai', '8', '余凯', 'Kai YU', 'Horizon Robotics创始人', '', '前百度研究院副院长，高级技术总监，深度学习研究院IDL创始人', '', 'Founder of Horizon Robotics', '', 'Former Vice President of Baidu Research Institute, Senior Technical Director and Founder of the Deep Learning Research Institute IDL.', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('35', 'zhanglei', '1', '张磊', 'Lei ZHANG', '高瓴资本集团的创始人', '高瓴资本董事长兼首席执行官', '作为一家专注于长期结构性价值投资的投资公司，高瓴资本目前已发展成为亚洲地区资产管理规模最大、业绩最优秀的投资基金之一', '让机器能够像人一样，能够更加智能的模糊思维，能够让人的幸福感更加提高。 ', 'Founder of Hillhouse Capital Group', 'Chairman of the board and CEO of Hillhouse Capital', 'With a focus on long-term structural investment, Hillhouse Capital has grown to become one of Asia\'s largest asset management companies and one of the investment funds with the best performance.', 'Let technology be more like the people - to increase more opaque intelligence allows humans prosperity to grow.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('36', 'zhangshoucheng', '2', '张首晟', 'Shoucheng ZHANG', '斯坦福大学物理系讲座教授', '', '清华大学高等研究院千人计划访问教授，美国艺术与科学学院院士', '我们今天正是要看到整个人类的未来，整个未来给我们带来的方向是什么。我们需要寻根，需要跨界的交流。', 'JG Jackson and CJ Wood Professor of Physics at Stanford University', '', 'Professor at Tsinghua University\'s Institute of Advanced Studies, Academician at the American Academy of Arts and Sciences', 'Today we will see the direction of the future. We must find the roots of the future and also create cross-border exchanges.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('37', 'zhangxike', '1', '张曦轲', 'Richard ZHANG', '安佰深全球合伙人', '安佰深大中华地区总裁', '曾任麦肯锡公司全球资深董事，上海分公司董事长，当年曾是麦肯锡全球合伙人评选委员会中唯一的华人委员，曾负责美国芝加哥分公司的合伙人评选工作，现任中兴通讯的独立董事', '我们这个未来论坛成立得恰当其时', 'Global Partner of Greater China of Apax Partners', 'President of Greater China of Apax Partners', 'Former Senior Director and Chairman of the Board of Directors of McKinsey & Co\'s Shanghai Branch and also the only Chinese member of McKinsey Global Partners Selection Committee. Formerly in charge of the Chicago branch of US McKinsey Partner Selection and current independent director of ZTE', 'The need for a Future Forum is now.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('38', 'zhangxingsheng', '1', '张醒生', 'Xingsheng ZHANG', '大自然保护协会亚太区首席代表', '道同资本创始合伙人', '老牛基金会理事长。曾任爱立信（中国）有限公司执行副总裁兼首席市场执行官；2003年加盟亚信，出任首席执行官（CEO）兼总裁', '互联网时代，使得空间不再是障碍。互联网正在创造一个人类崭新的未来。', 'Chief Representative of TNC Asia', 'Co-Founder of China United Capital', 'Chairman of the Stella Foundation, Former Executive Vice President and Chief Marketing Officer of Ericcson China Co Ltd. In 2003, Zhang joined CICA and served as President and CEO.', 'Space is now no longer a constraint in the Internet era. The Internet is creating a new future for mankind.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('39', 'zhaoyong', '8', '赵勇', 'Yong ZHAO', '格灵深瞳联合创始人', '', '计算机视觉和人工智能专家', '我们用人工智能一步一步改变世界', 'Co-Founder of DeepGlint', '', 'Expert in Visual and Artificial Intelligence', 'We can use artificial intelligence to change the world step by step.');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('40', 'zhuyunlai', '2', '朱云来', 'Levin ZHU', '金融专业人士', '', '金融专业人士.曾任瑞士信贷第一波士顿高级副总裁、中国国际金融有限公司董事长。', '经济发展最重要的是需要靠科技来驱动，社会的进步一定要有科技实质性的成长', 'Financial Specialist', '', 'Former Senior Vice President of Credit Suisse Boston, Chairman of the China International Capital Co.', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('43', 'shenxiangyang', '1', '沈向洋', 'Harry Shum', '微软全球执行副总裁', '', '', '', 'Microsoft Executive Vice President', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('44', 'maxuezheng', '1', '马雪征', 'Ma Xuezheng', '博裕资本管理公司 董事长', '', '', '', 'Chairman of Bo Yu Capital Management Company', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('46', 'likaifu', '1', '李开复', 'KaiFu Lee', '创新工场董事长&CEO', '', '李开复博士于2009年9月在中国北京创立创新工场，帮助中国青年成功创业，创新工场立足互联网、移动互联网和云计算等领域。在此之前，李开复博士曾就职于Google、微软、苹果等世界顶尖科技公司，并分别担任全球副总裁职务。李博士曾以最高荣誉毕业于哥伦比亚大学，并于1988年获得卡内基梅隆大学电脑学博士学位。', '', 'CEO and Chairman of Innovation Works', '', 'Innovation Works was founded in September 2009 in Beijing to help young Chinese entrepreneurs succeed. Prior to this, Dr. Lee has worked at Google, Microsoft, Apple and Pinnacle Technology Corp. Dr. Lee graduated from Columbia University with the highest of honors and received a doctorate in Computer Science from Carnegie Mellon University in 1988.', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('47', 'wenxiaogang', '4', '文小刚', 'Wen XiaoGang', '理论物理学家、美国麻省理工学院终身教授', '', '', '', 'Tenured Professor of Theoretical Physics at Massachusetts Institute of Technology', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `people` VALUES ('48', 'zhoukui', '1', '周逵 ', 'Zhou Kui', '红杉资本 合伙人', '', '周逵，红杉资本中国基金合伙人。投资方向覆盖TMT、医疗健康、清洁技术和消费服务等领域，他直接负责投资的许多早、中期公司已发展成为各细分市场的领导企业，其中近十家成为美国、香港和中国A股资本市场的上市公司。在2005年加入红杉之前，周逵曾在联想投资公司和联想集团任职，并有多年中小企业工作经验。', '', 'Partner of Sequoia Capital', '', 'Kui Zhou is a partner of Sequoia Capital China. His investment focus covers TMT, healthcare, clean technologies, consumer services and etc. Many early-stage and intermediate-stage companies invested under his direct command have developed into leading enterprises in their specific field, and about ten of them have even become public companies in A capital markets of the U.S., and Hong Kong or mainland of China. Prior to joining Sequoia Capital China in 2005, Kui Zhou had served in Legend Capital and Lenovo Group with years of work experience in SMEs. ', '');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for `people_category`
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `people_category`;
CREATE TABLE `people_category` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `value` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `title_zh-cn` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `title_en` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `note_zh-cn` varchar(400) NOT NULL,
  `note_en` varchar(400) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of people_category
-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `people_category` VALUES ('1', '.founder', '1', '理事', 'Council', '具有良好社会声誉、有理想、有思想并具有影响力的商界、科学界和教育界卓越人士。', 'Prestigious leaders in Chinese business, government, venture capital, technology and the sciences.');
INSERT INTO `people_category` VALUES ('2', '.advisor', '2', '咨询委员会', 'Consultative Committee', '对未来论坛有共识，于所在领域有一定成就，有理想、情怀、思想和追求，并在未来论坛工作做出过积极贡献的人士以及其他各界知名人士。', 'Accomplished and well-know personages and contributors who have consensus of the Future Forum.');
INSERT INTO `people_category` VALUES ('3', '.scientist', '4', '科学家顾问委员会', 'Scientific Committee', '蜚声中外的世界级科学家。', 'Renowned scientists.');
INSERT INTO `people_category` VALUES ('4', '.entrepreneur', '8', '青年行动小组', 'Youth Action Group', '一群40岁以下中国最具影响力的互联网先行者，投资界成功者、科学界前沿者，同时是具有前沿思考的青年创业者、创新思维模式的科学家。透过此交流平台，鼓励并支持新生代青年的创业发想及理念。', 'Leaders and influencers aged under 40 from the business, government and academic fields who encourages the young generation’s entrepreneurial ideal.');
INSERT INTO `people_category` VALUES ('5', '*', '0', '未来/人物', 'Future/People', '未来论坛聚集了时下中国最具影响力的互联网先行者，投资家和科学界前沿者，其中既有李彦宏、杨元庆，徐小平、丁健、沈南鹏、张磊等工商界翘楚，也有施一公、饶毅、张首晟等蜚声中外的顶尖科学家。', '');

